result.name: Shatin Chicken Congee

reviews.text: Amazing chicken coogee and fried pigeon!! Coogee is super smooth and yummy.
Nice chicken congee and it's got a cozy mezzanie

Quite basic eatery with canteen style tables covered in plastic sheets. Food tasty and mid priced and service friendly. Staff try their best to be chatty...lol.
Pigeon good but higher priced than most similar competition. Seems a local favourite but not a big place so may entail wait for a table.
Check bill carefully as a bit casual with calculations.
It food os ok, the place is a bit messy with lots of people shouting while eating. A noisy place, but it is part of the local culture sence.
The dish size does not match with the high price.

result.adr_address: 香港大圍積存街12號
result.name: 沙田強記雞粥

reviews.text: 好食👍

沙田強記雞粥
好掛著😻沙田嘅雞粥🐔
-

小妹間唔中會突然想食某啲嘢，今日放工後，又突然好掛著沙田嘅雞粥🐔。橫掂今日有揸車🚗，睇下泊唔泊到門口位先，有就食喇😼。

So lucky 泊到門口位😎， 就係呢間喇。

有成年無嚟食喇， 環境依舊咁街坊🙊。

Menu 都一樣📃， 即係價錢都無變到喇。

輕食住我最想食嘅3樣嘢先😋。

雞粥🐔［1碗］（$35）
外表平凡，雞肉夠、夠嫩滑，多粥底夠綿👍。

紅燒乳鴿（$75）
雖然價錢貴過出面， 但絕對值得。
外脆內軟， 乳鴿肉汁比外皮鎖住😋。 夠曬juicy😍。

豉油皇炒麵🥢（$45）
我條條都入曬味， 麵條軟硬度適中。

飲埋杯茶🍵先，飽哂😽。

==========

沙田強記雞粥
地址: 大圍積存街12號地下

菜色很好，味道很正！特別花雕焗乳鵾，和鷄粥！人比較多！若带酒入內自用！要特別加開瓶费用哩！
、
食物一般，不過風味十足
Amazing chicken coogee and fried pigeon!! Coogee is super smooth and yummy.
